%h2 Options

%p The Resolute comes in two sizes, regular and extra-large. The main difference between the two is the handle size. Some people, men in particular, have very large hands and have a hard time finding knives that are comfortable. The XL model is made to suit those requirements. If you find that most everyday object feel too small to you then order the XL version, otherwise order the regular version.

%p Customers also have the option to choose different colors for the handle scales on their knife. The handle can be a solid color (like you see on the brown-handled knife below), or it can have contrasting liners (like seen on the tan and red knife below). Handles are only available in G10 as I believe it's the best material for the job. There are a number of colors available:

