%h2 Ordering

%p I don't keep any knives in stock, as they're each made to meet individual customer requirements. Because I only make knives part-time it's very hard for me to give you an exact time of delivery for the knife. So instead each customer is added to the  production list in order, when I am able to start work on your knife I contact you to re-confirm your order, then I make the knife to your specifications. Wait time is about 2-4 weeks per person on the list (approx 20-30 weeks right now). However I do not guarantee delivery dates. This is because making each knife takes quite a while, and I want to make sure that I have enough time to make each knife to meet my exacting personal standards.

